{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NTM5OTg1MzMy", "number": 6008, "title": "[ISSUE 5541] Fix H2 in-memory database table missing issues", "bodyText": "Fix H2 in-memory database table missing issues\n\n\n Explain briefly about why the bug exists and how to fix it.\nJust add ;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1 to the database URL for H2StorageConfig\nSee the In-Memory Databases section of the Features page. To quote:\n\nBy default, closing the last connection to a database closes the database. For an in-memory database, this means the content is lost. To keep the database open, add ;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1 to the database URL. To keep the content of an in-memory database as long as the virtual machine is alive, use jdbc:h2:mem:test;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1.\n\n\n\n If this pull request closes/resolves/fixes an existing issue, replace the issue number. Closes #5541\n\n\n Update the CHANGES log.", "createdAt": "2020-12-15T05:25:14Z", "url": "https://github.com/apache/skywalking/pull/6008", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "957d549b68421dbf772ea30a1afc72dc824ba918"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-12-15T08:05:04Z", "author": {"login": "coolbeevip"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 6, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdmTKvSgH2gAyNTM5OTg1MzMyOjRiZjA2ZDNmNmRlNmY5YjQxY2UyMTM5MzEwMGE2OTZiNTk5YjZiYWI=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdmUJXGgFqTU1MjEzNDE5OQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "4bf06d3f6de6f9b41ce21393100a696b599b6bab", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/apache/skywalking/commit/4bf06d3f6de6f9b41ce21393100a696b599b6bab", "committedDate": "2020-12-15T05:06:17Z", "message": "add ;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1 to the database URL"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "8df6628bbcc402971d1a407e6f35b419906460dc", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/apache/skywalking/commit/8df6628bbcc402971d1a407e6f35b419906460dc", 